            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">古德里安同曼施坦因与隆美尔不同，他的文字里述说政治的成分远大于后者，我很难把它看成纯粹的战史参考。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="725413067">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-725413067" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-725413067" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="725413067">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/harrychen723/">Ranger</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-12-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">同为普鲁士军事传统的践行者，却又对该传统的弊端洞若观火，战术素养堪为德军军官翘楚，历史机缘巧合所造就的闪击英雄。全局战略眼光虽逊于曼施坦因，著述水准和可读性则更胜一筹</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="677627106">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-677627106" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-677627106" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="677627106">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tudousky/">土豆斯基今天要</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-05-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">怀疑删节 这书对希特勒评价比我想象的高。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

